				<div id="content">
					<p class="home_welcome">
						Welcome to the 
						<img src="images/cal.png" alt="CAL" class="cal" />
						cierge online gateway to campus and community resources. 
					</p>
					<p>
						<img src="images/cal.png" alt="CAL" class="cal" />
						cierge, offered through UC Berkeley&rsquo;s Office of the 
						<a href="http://vpaafw.chance.berkeley.edu/" target="_blank">
							Vice Provost for the Faculty</a>, supports the recruitment and retention of faculty. CALcierge services include both relocation services to prospective and new faculty and dual career services for the accompanying faculty spouse or partner as well as to the spouses or partners who are part of the University faculty retention effort. 
					</p>
					<p>
						To request 
						<img src="images/cal.png" alt="CAL" class="cal" />
						cierge services, faculty candidates or departments conducting a faculty search should contact this office via email at 
						<a href="mailto:calcierge@berkeley.edu">
							calcierge@berkeley.edu</a>. 
					</p>
					<img src="images/home_circles.png" alt="quotes" class="home_circles" />
